{"tid":878122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發：美國炸彈郵包案疑犯黨籍由民主突變共和！","createTime":"2018-10-27T01:16:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T04:35:45.000Z","uid":70063,"like":134,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"7400204dc18b4cc7082a14195201129b2f9b92ff","tid":878122,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T01:16:24.000Z","msg":"美國聯邦密探在三小時前拘捕疑犯凱蕯&middot;沙郁 (Cesar Sayoc)，涉嫌關乎最近寄炸彈郵包畀民主黨希拉利，奧巴馬，索羅斯，CNN，克林頓。沙郁現年五十六，有暴力案底，擁van仔貼滿親特朗普反民主黨標語畫像。但美國有心水清網民發現沙郁在社交網站 <a href=\"http://mylife.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmylife.com&d=9iVdLhF2oXh1GoYoeFC2uozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=66ee14eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">mylife.com</a>的個人資料黨籍一欄本來寫民主黨，今日在幾分鐘內突變共和黨! (<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10211767549615486&amp;set=p.10211767549615486&amp;type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10211767549615486%26set%3Dp.10211767549615486%26type%3D3%26theater&d=9iVdLhF2oXh1GoYoeFC2uozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=627498ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10211767549615486&amp;set=p.10211767549615486&amp;type=3&amp;theater</a>)<br />\n<br />\n而且據CNN拍攝，寄畀CNN的炸彈郵包郵費不足，郵票無郵戳，回郵地址寫Florids，應為FLORIDA(佛羅理達州)之誤，疑犯本身真箇居佛羅理州，有無咁蠢自報家門呢？(參 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=2082381702092323&amp;set=a.1384742905189543&amp;type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D2082381702092323%26set%3Da.1384742905189543%26type%3D3%26theater&d=9iVdLhF2oXh1GoYoeFC2uozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=24c3e599\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=2082381702092323&amp;set=a.1384742905189543&amp;type=3&amp;theater</a> )　<br />\n<br />\n又nbcnews話沙郁係共和黨註冊選民，然而佛羅理達州根本不容有重罪案底者投票。<br />\n<br />\n另有美國網民問: 中期選舉下月舉行，真正共和黨支持者有無咁笨，高調寄炸彈郵包畀民主黨人，令選民覺得係共和黨做的呢？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/2018/10/cesar-sayoc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2F2018%2F10%2Fcesar-sayoc%2F&d=9iVdLhF2oXh1GoYoeFC2uozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=385b4631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.localpresshk.com/2018/10/cesar-sayoc/</a>"},{"pid":"72a4b3996efd36c14f4a93339971b293c2d80cb9","tid":878122,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T01:20:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e4806eecbd7e556be0ab7ef79fcae39134a96a1","tid":878122,"uid":176991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T01:21:47.000Z","msg":"張圖左邊都睇唔到profile個id<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3092898afb3d0ab023931520a70d7e49d4840b53","tid":878122,"uid":49392,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T01:21:59.000Z","msg":"五毛：又話美國民主，香港連囚犯都有投票權"},{"pid":"d448c4588fa964d1a28a3bf5ee60f5dcbb173bbb","tid":878122,"uid":34410,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T01:22:01.000Z","msg":"fake news <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7961b3507032cb1de39566a37da01368a38f17f1","tid":878122,"uid":21028,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T01:23:30.000Z","msg":"有時 做呢啲野 會反效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b3166988fdbfd743bf5ad41fce5f789cc07e6ee","tid":878122,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T01:27:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41cf7ee5f27d99c8057dc930f4242d09557c9422","tid":878122,"uid":134071,"like":6,"di